content_request: Quelle est l'évolution du trafic data

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT 
    rcdm.year AS year, 
    rcdm.month AS month,
    SUM(rcdm.volumes) AS total_volume_data,
    SUM(rcdm.parc_data_facturer) AS total_clients
FROM 
    reporting_ca_data_monthly AS rcdm
JOIN 
    (SELECT MAX(year) AS max_year FROM reporting_ca_data_monthly) AS max_year_subquery 
    ON rcdm.year = max_year_subquery.max_year
WHERE 
    rcdm.segment_marche IN ('JEUNES', 'ENTRANT', 'MILIEU DE MARCHE', 'HAUT DE MARCHE', 'TRES HAUT DE MARCHE')
GROUP BY 
    rcdm.year, rcdm.month
ORDER BY 
    rcdm.year DESC, rcdm.month DESC;
donne moi le ca seddo d'Octobre 2024 à Mai 2025

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT 
    rcm.year AS year, 
    rcm.month AS month, 
    SUM(rcm.ca_seddo) AS ca_seddo_total
FROM 
    reporting_ca_monthly AS rcm
WHERE 
    (rcm.year = 2024 AND rcm.month >= 10) 
    OR 
    (rcm.year = 2025 AND rcm.month <= 5)
GROUP BY 
    rcm.year, 
    rcm.month
ORDER BY 
    rcm.year ASC, 
    rcm.month ASC;
Donne moi le parc actif orange de 2025

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT 
    parc.year AS year, 
    parc.month AS month, 
    SUM(parc.parc_90days) AS total_parc_actif 
FROM 
    reporting_daily_parc AS parc 
WHERE 
    parc.year = 2025 
GROUP BY 
    parc.year, 
    parc.month 
ORDER BY 
    parc.year DESC, 
    parc.month DESC;
donne moi le ca des offres illimix

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT 
    ds.year AS year,
    ds.month AS month,
    SUM(ds.sous_mnt) AS total_ca_illimix
FROM 
    daily_souscription AS ds
WHERE 
    ds.year = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE()) 
    AND ds.offer_name LIKE '%ILLIMIX%'
GROUP BY 
    ds.year, ds.month
ORDER BY 
    ds.year DESC, ds.month DESC;
